Martha Stewart Living Omnimedia Logo Martha Stewart Living Omnimedia Inc. is a diversified media and merchandising company founded by Martha Stewart and owned by Marquee Brands LLC since April 2019. It is organized into four business segments: publishing, Internet, broadcasting media platforms, and merchandising product lines. MSO’s business holdings include a variety of print publications, television and radio programming, and e-commerce websites. Source
